### GitHub Projects:

* **Elmstagram** - A basic UI-clone of Instagram using Elm
  * [GitHub](https://github.com/bkbooth/Elmstagram)
  * [Demo](https://elmstagram.bkbooth.me)
  * [Building a basic UI-clone of Instagram using Elm - Part 1](https://bkbooth.me/building-a-basic-ui-clone-of-instagram-using-elm-part-1/)
  * [Part 2](https://bkbooth.me/building-a-basic-ui-clone-of-instagram-using-elm-part-2/)
  * [Part 3](https://bkbooth.me/building-a-basic-ui-clone-of-instagram-using-elm-part-3/)
* **promise** - A JavaScript Promise implementation
  * [GitHub](https://github.com/bkbooth/promise)
  * [Writing a JavaScript Promises Library](https://bkbooth.me/writing-a-javascript-promises-library/)
* **BlockDrop** - A shameless Tetris clone using HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript
  * [GitHub](https://github.com/bkbooth/BlockDrop)
  * [Demo](https://blockdrop.bkbooth.me/)
